  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is limited to Class II spinal fixation devices evaluated under quasi-static compression-bending loading per ASTM F1717 at room temperature. Model risk is assessed at Level 3 and the overall assurance level is Medium.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/astm-f1717-compression-bending",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-predicts-f1717-compression-bending",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/model/pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/lab1-experimental-constructs",
    "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/data/lab2-experimental-constructs"
  ],
